	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=201005><span id= >GaliemVaelant</span></a><br><span id=notbold>221 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.96]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Young warriors, don't be discouraged by the fact that some people rate down this quest.&nbsp;&nbsp;It simply means there is better out there, but this quest may still be right for you.<br><br>If you aren't of level, and have someone to help, this is a great weapon for your secondary slot (off hand) that doesn't cost any platinum at all to get!  That one factor makes this quest worth it for some people 8)<br><br>However, if you would like to see what people are talking about in these posts, check the links below.  I remember when I was new to EQ, I would look at forums like this, and say stuff like &quot;Wow!  That's great info, but WTF is a lammy?  Like a shammy?&quot;  Hope this helped someone out there 8)<br><br>Centi Longsword:<br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7137" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7137</a><br><br>Wurmslayer, or &quot;Wurmy&quot;:<br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=355" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=355</a><br><br>Lamentation, or &quot;Lammy&quot;:<br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=313" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=313</a><br><br>If you're under the level to do the quest for the Soldier's Sword, I applaud your researching already 8) You'd be surprised how many people in game believe you have to play 24/7 to learn anything, when everything you could possibly want to know is right here 8)<br><br>If you can't get any of these, don't despair!  The hunt for gear can be frustrating, I know, but there is an answer, at least for weapons.  In Gulf of Gunthak, there are many decent weapons that usually rot at the pirate camps.  Maybe if you ask nice, one of the higher level peeps will sell one too ya 8)  Here's a link to the equipment list for that zone:<br><br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/itemzone.html?zone=179" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/itemzone.html?zone=179</a><br><br>Much luck to ya 8)<br>**edit added centi... how could we forget our preciousssss?**<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Mar  4 09:39:01 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>--Pay attention to the cracked streets and the broken homes.. Some call it slums, some call it nice! I wanna take you to a wasteland I like to call my home.. Welcome to paradise!</td></tr>
