	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=16724><span id= >Lady AngelsynWhitewings</span></a><br><span id=notbold>512 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.56]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I keep getting conflicting reports on off-hand weapon viability...&nbsp;&nbsp;Some people say that only the Damage on the off-hand weapon matters, others say you should have a similar delay in your off-hand as your main hand.<br><br>Assuming that the off-hand weapon delay doesn't matter, this would be a very decent weapon for off-hand use.  Decent damage &amp; some nice stats.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
